# RULE-004: Asset Mapping (Critical)

- **No `"Satoshi Variable"`** — do not use this font reference.
- **Map `"Lexend Mega"`** → `.font-lexend-mega`.
- **Map `"Roboto"`** → `.font-roboto`.
- **Flag missing variables** with `/* VAR_NEEDED: [name] */` when a design variable is not yet defined.

Use these class/variable mappings consistently in styles and components.
